      "span_text": "The major findings of the present study are as follows: (1) Expression of SDF-1 on the surface of adherent platelets is increased and mediates rolling and firm adhesion of CD34 ϩ progenitor cells on immobilized platelets under flow conditions in vitro and at sites of vascular injury in vivo. [CITATION_1]"
